<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1436,152,298]" box="[151,218,152,177]" pageId="7" pageNumber="66">
<emphasis box="[151,218,152,177]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="66">Notes</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1436,152,298]" pageId="7" pageNumber="66">
The presence of four setae on the sternal shield, the fusion of the peritrematal shields with exopodals IV, well developed presternals, as well as 
<number box="[605,620,232,258]" pageId="7" pageNumber="66" value="2.0">2</number>
pairs of pre-anal setae on the ventri-anal shield and size of idiosoma are good diagnostic characters for this new species.
</paragraph>
